{"tid":201904,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"G唔G持連囝將波台正名為「香討台」？","createTime":"2017-04-15T06:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T07:06:50.000Z","uid":90863,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbef3b3a1a857e6a1b4571a38245531d58d785de","tid":201904,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"明明波台ching引入香討文化活化連登功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n典知就成日比cc台辣殺屌5p字喊打喊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住響波台貼下新聞話下麻友係G又要加張九唔搭八足球gif驚比連囝bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如直頭將體育台改名做香討台，等香討特有文化可以係連登得到保存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n波台ching開post又可以講乜都得唔止限於體育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：支持<br />\n負評：樓主好波"},{"pid":"a9da3fdaa866e14443937f9f81d873254f3640db","tid":201904,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"你呢d人係咪真係咁鐘意引人注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好可憐"},{"pid":"2404808abadcbd917a3980a880ca56d52345b405","tid":201904,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢d人係咪真係咁鐘意引人注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好可憐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/142717_cc1e414d4d774cb0e244aeb1689c9c31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F142717_cc1e414d4d774cb0e244aeb1689c9c31.jpg&h=dda10fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYes"},{"pid":"1eeaa9904d8bdd85764634fe9855beee201dbfef","tid":201904,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:53:38.0